NOTE FOR PROSPECTIVE BUYERS / LICENSEES

If you are evaluating this codebase for acquisition or licensing:

- This file is a placeholder asserting ownership and is NOT a substitute for
  a proper sale/licensing agreement. Terms of sale (exclusivity, scope of use,
  source-code transfer vs. hosted-license, ongoing support commitments, and
  the specific IP being transferred) should be defined in a separate contract
  between buyer and seller before any code, credentials, or infrastructure
  access changes hands.
- Third-party services this project integrates with (Midtrans, Biteship,
  Fonnte, Cloudinary, Resend, Supabase, Sentry, PostHog, Upstash) are each
  under their own separate terms of service — this license does not grant,
  transfer, or imply any rights to those third-party services. A buyer will
  need their own accounts/API credentials with each provider they intend to
  keep using post-transfer.
- See ARCHITECTURE.md for a technical overview and BUYER_TECHNICAL_OVERVIEW.md
  for a due-diligence-oriented summary of what's implemented, tested, and
  known-incomplete as of the last audit.
